node.text: ✨A huge THANK YOU to everyone for all the support you’ve shown me these last two weeks!✨💕My new decor received such an amazing response and unfortunately there’s been an alarming amount of scam ads popping up on Facebook, Instagram and Etsy using my content! They’re also using my descriptions to trick buyers into thinking they’re an extension of my shop. My handmade decor is only available through my site sacraluna(link in bio). My Instagram is Sacraluna and my tiktok is Sacralunajewelry. If you see these ads using my videos, please do not buy! Report, Tag me or send me screenshots so I can report the post directly. So far I’ve removed over 58 ads and I’m trying my best to help those who purchased from these sites get a refund. The sites will usually have a huge discount for the item like $28.99! but not have any detailed photos. Just screenshots from my page. This became a huge issue for me on TikTok since many were questioning if I was even the real creator. Luckily my Instagram showcases my work for the last 9 years and documents the progress of my journey as an artist. I’ve posted videos of my apartment countless times in my stories. My cats, my tattoos and my studio. This battle of taking down scammers has been going on for about 5 months but luckily I have the best support system and I cannot be more grateful for all of you!!!😭💕💕Thank you all so much for defending me, sharing my work in your stories, posting me on your page, just chatting with me when you know I’m feeling overwhelmed. I am blessed to have you all in my life 😭💕

node.text: Is it true Instagram will no longer be a photo sharing app??!!😵I’ve noticed a massive drop in views on my photos recently and after posting about it this week the top comment was instagrams newest update. So I did some research and found that although the app will still allow photos to be shared, it’s main goal is to be more like TikTok. Focusing more on promoting reels and videos. I honestly wish Instagram would stop changing everything about this app and give us back the chronological feed💔Thank you all again for commenting on my recent post and dm’ing me about this issue. Have a blessed day everyone !!!🌸✨
